asset_description: Welcome! My name is Ares. My favourite topic of conversation is Thomas Edison. I once kicked John F. Kennedy Jr for one dance, got a Hennessy in my hand. I try to bury that memory deep in the litterbox of my mind. I love playing The Sims. Wanna join me?

I'm here, I'm bad at rhymes, I'm Kitty Pride #917! Be proud, be vivid, and be yourself. I could tone it down, but then I'd be lion to myself. Of course, not everyone can afford to be as colourful as I am, but I'm lucky — one of my ancestors was a non-binary landowner and there was gold in them/their hills.
Salaam. I'm Kitty #575183. Just between us, I sometimes hang out with a platypus. I have an unhealthy obsession with dijon mustard. We're so fur-tunate to have found each other!

*yawn* Sorry, you caught me napping. I'm called Captain Flirtydrop. I've wandered this planet in search of a ghost, but so far, all I have found is spicy salami. To be honest, tripping my owner is all I'm really interested in. Meowza.
Noice. My name is Kira Canrue. I love to wear hintomint. I'm trying to consume at least one serving of salad every day. It's a newer health thing I read about on the web. Good talk, catch ya later!
来了啊？. 我的大名就是 MagnificentTerror！经常有人说我有哈利波特的个性，好像真的是这样。 本喵绝对会为了为了吃到最后一片披萨 而放弃一切。 如果你和本喵一样喜欢 牛仔热裤 ，我们一定可以成为好朋友。
Top o' the muffin to ya. Duke Yappywidgey is the name, swiping right is the game. I went to school with Thomas O'Malley The Alley Cat, back then that was one magical cat. Hurry, we haven't much time.
Noice. Hiya. *winces*. I'm Sugar Grogmoo. In another life, I think I would have been a emu. I love playing The Sims. Wanna join me?
Uh, hi! I'm Founder Cat 67. I'm a professional Spin Instructor  and I love cereal. It's not common knowledge, but my ancestry connects me to Princess Diana. I hope we can be raunchy friends.
Heyo! Kitty #454634 here. I'm here to enjoy chasing red dots and breakdancing. When I'm not practicing witchcraft, I'm riverdancing! Will you be the garlic butter to my cinammon?
你好呀！. 本尊我叫 Trilly Olesmoochie，我这辈子就只讨厌新疆羊肉串，没别的。 本喵一般上都穿 内衣 ，所以当你发现我只穿喵外套时，肯定是发生了什么怪事。 相信我，你将会日久见喵心。
Enchanté! I'm Nero Greyheart, at least that's what they're calling me these days. Can you scratch my cuticle? I'm too lazy to do it myself. What's that smell?
奥嗨唷！. 本喵爬不更名，坐不改姓，就叫 THUNDER-CEMENT CAT！我的表哥是喵星球鼎鼎大名的凯蒂猫。 如果你也喜欢 抗议资本主义，那我们一定很合得来！ 本喵希望你也和我一样喜欢可爱喵星宝宝。
Yo. I'm Bandit Ticksmoosh. Pleased to meet you. I was the real world inspiration for Tony Soprano. Gahhh, aren't you cute!

*hissing noises*! My name's Kitty #399200. I once peed on John F. Kennedy Jr.'s cat. They had it coming. It wasn't heavily publicized, but I once had a brief relationship with Puss in Boots. This will be an amewsing friendship.

*hissing noises*! I'm Kitty #85337. In high school, I was voted school jock. When no one's home, I invite my pals over and we listen to Aretha Franklin. I look forward to spinning sick beats with you.
饭吃了没？. 从小，大伙儿都叫我 1st Gen Pink Panther！若你也喜欢收集迷人的T恤，不如我们安排个时间见面吧！ 如果你也喜欢 跟着直播学化妆，那我们一定很合得来！ 让我俩一起领悟喵真理吧！

Salutations. My name is Joyful Griddles. You might not believe it, but I've seen a shapeshifter before, and it was actually very lovely. I like to tell stories, which are often either mysterious or oblivious. You and I must have met in another life.
Bark...errr, meow. I'm Lencho Lubway. Color me orangesoda, I'm thrilled to be in your life! I eat in my sleep, I hope that's not going to be a problem.
Uh, hi. I'm Puss Purrface, at least that's what they're calling me these days. Whenever I heard The Cure it makes me think of ice cream. Show me whatchu got!
Top of the mornin' to ya. I'm Duke Zippyrubin. Step into my office. I'd give anything to hang out with Michael Cera. My only policy is no politics.
Aloha. My name is Sixten Hornsire 5/5. I pretty much only listen to Migos. My parents fed me wasabi when I was a kid and I refuse to eat it now. My nose is itchy and I can't reach. Would you mind?

Good morning. My name is Kitty #797019. I can't wait to hear all about your favourite condiments! Mine are thousand island dressing and garlic butter. If you want to join me and my clique, you should know that on Wednesdays we wear pink. I’m lost. Can you give me directions to your heart?

Howdy! My name is Lala Wasabiheart. I'm wondrous, you're adventurous, let's connect. If you look closely into my eyes, you'll see hints of my lineage as a gorgon. I can't believe you'd show your face around here.
*tips hat*. I'm Karima Goosepooka. And you are? During my kitten days, I snuggled Jerry Seinfeld. If you can prove I can fly, I can touch the sky then I'll eat my beanies right here, right now.

Sup playa. My name is Lapis: 💙 Drift 💙 Alien, Arc., which got me teased a lot in high school. I combine the best qualities of Jeff Goldblum, King Louis XIV, and NSYNC. Let's go invest in a condo together.

I'm Pawrula The Bright #397, and I’m on a mission to bridge the distance between academia and industry, so we can all do for value what the internet did for information. Like a cat walking on a keyboard, we'll be an unstoppable force — a collective pushing the whole forward. Sometimes I feel like a crusader leading the charge, but other times I feel like a nap in the sunshine, so there's a lot going on.

Buen día. Mi nombre es Al, and I may seem like I have my head in the clouds, but you can't pull the wool over my eyes. I'm only looking for friendships with chill vibes. If you're looking for drama, go talk to a llama.

Greetings, kind purr! My name's Page and I'm a very good and clever kitten with a lot to offer the world! I have squired with the greatest of knights: there was Sir Face (they were a bit shallow), Sir Port (a very kind cat), and of course, Sir Prise (she was amazing). And now I have you! Gosh! I must be the luckiest kitten in the world!
Yo! I'm Mister Sleepybip. I'm bashful, you're woke, let's connect. All I want in life is to listen to my Hanson CDs in peace. Is that too much to ask? Will you help me with my resumé?

Rise and grind! My name is Mister Wonderfrou. Let's get to know each other better. I once debated with Chairman Mao because some people just want to watch the world burn. I try to bury that memory deep in the litterbox of my mind. Word on the street is Zelda is the best game of all time. All time!
Good day! I'm Myeong Sadbinky. I like long walks around my litter box. I once entered a litter-eating contest just to ride an ostrich. I did not win. Does anyone even use Neopets anymore?
哩好！! 我我我叫 BlueLagoonKi！别人都说我我我勇敢，但如果你问我我我，我我我觉得自己其实更聪明绝顶啦！ 我吃任何食物都要放草莓果酱 ，真的。比如三明治、 冰激凌、 辛拉面— 任何食物。 一起畅玩喵趴吧！

I might appear to be a simple talisman, but if you take me into the realm of the Citadel you can reveal my true power: they call me VIRGIN: Purebred Tally. Shiny!! No god can control me, but all will try. And if they succeed in collecting every talisman, who knows what power they could wield?
Ciao. I'm Shadow Kingnoggin, a lover of all things orange. I honestly would rather do anything else besides watch Deuce Bigalow: Male Gigolo. Will you help me with my resumé?

Mahalo! I'm called Mack Saucyway. I like long walks on the beach and pico de gallo. I think I would have been voted "most likely to work at NASA" if I had stayed in school. Will you brush my tail? I like it brushed three times a day.
Greetings! I'm Yaya Warydub! I enjoy long walks and coughing up furballs. I used to love sleeping in fresh laundry, until the accident. Goodnight.

How's it going. They call me Missy Grogson. Hey, got any crispy chicken skin on you? I'm always hungry. Imagine me as John F. Kennedy Jr's more smelly sibling. I used to be a Skydiving Instructor until I hurt my fur.

Salutations. Folks call me Thank you from CryptoKitties. No one actually knows my real name, they just know how atomic I am. I'm trying to consume at least one serving of sardines every day. It's a newer health thing I read about on the web. One time I beat Mr. Bigglesworth in an arm wrestle.
*hissing noises*! I'm Kitty #447315. I believe that one day cats will rule this planet. I'm often described as vegan, and I own it. I can't wait to wake you up at 4am for seemingly no reason.
*hissing noises*! Kitty #380920 here. I'm here to enjoy reciting poetry and tricking babies. My friends describe me as "stinky." It's... accurate. Will you be the peanut butter to my cinammon?
Namaste. I'm Señor Soulrubin. I drank martinis with Backstreet Boys when I was younger, but those days are gone. I like meowing for no reason at all at the lunar new year. À Bientôt!
*winces*, I am Taters Pharoahfu, devoted friend of the patagonian mara. Can you scratch my solar plexus? I'm too lazy to do it myself. Someday, all of this will be yours.
Rise and grind. Countess Soulsniggle? Haven't heard that name in years. I ate raisins with fancy mustard on it and now my tummy hurts. You and I go together like hamburgers and bbq marinade.

Good day. My name is Kitty #846219. Let's cut to the chase: I like stalking crows. Wanna join? I'm thinking of dying my fur a metallic shade of grey. Do you think it will suit me? You're going to need a lot of wine for this relationship to be tolerable.

*hissing noises*. I'm Kitty #529355. I collect snap-backs and I love cucumber salad. I once dreamed of being a Private Dancer. Now I can be found knitting mittens all day. Honey, you wouldn't wanna see these claws come out.
Shalom! I'm G14 Scarlet. I've never told anyone this, but I once kissed a dog. My great-great-great-great-great-great grandkitty lived with King Henry VIII. I hope we can be pawmates.
Hello! I'm Dreamia, feline warrior of a magical realm I can't tell you about. I've never actually finished Pitch Perfect, I get too distracted with tripping my owner. My only policy is no politics.

Yarr matey. I'm Kali X Floorislava. RARE COMBO, and I will do almost anything to run a hamster farm. I was going to become a Paranormal Investigator, but then I found out the world is flat. If you can prove my parents are aliens then I'll eat my smoking jacket right here, right now.

How goes it. My name is President Fluffychimp. I love to wear taupe. Sometimes, when I'm fighting the patriarchy, I can't help but think about the cuddly gremlin. I've spent the last few years perfecting my chocolate recipe. Wanna try it?

Hi friend, my name is Missy Softhands, but you may address me as supreme cat overlord. I combine the best qualities of Shia LaBeouf, Confucius, and Childish Gambino. Let's pump some Weezer and get busy!

En Taro Adun. I'm Angel Spicysmookie. I'm magnificent and turbulent, and sometimes even wondrous. I was voted "Most fabulous" at my office Christmas party. Will you brush my tail? I like it brushed three times a day.
What's up! I'm Kitty #349702. I enjoy riding unicorns, eating until I loathe myself, and reciting poetry. My friends describe me as "voluptuous." It's... accurate. I hope we can be pawmates.
Hi-ya! My name's Peach Googly Jaguar!!. I once peed on Marie Antoinette's cat. They had it coming. I once made a chimpanzee pester. We're so fur-tunate to have found each other!

Dia dhuit, I'm Clover_568! Oof, I rode in here on a rainbow and those things aren't as soft as they look. Have you seen my pot o' gold? I swear I left it right here... Oh well, I don't need piles o' shinies to know I'm the luckiest cat in the KittyVerse––I get to hang out with you!

RAWR XD! Allow me to introduce myself. I am Qattus Sprinkledaze and I am very well known for sharing memes and catching leprechauns. My hobbies include rearranging price tags at the supermarket, but only in moderation. If you can prove politicians are aliens then I'll eat my cargo pants right here, right now.
Bonjour. I'm Henna Wolfgrey, a dark Kitty of the night. I was the real world inspiration for Ross Geller. Talk to the paw.

Jambo. My name is Virgin: Neon Martian.. As a young kitten, I was always tricking babies, but I think I've grown out of that. Did you know if you wish on a falling star it will come to life and marry you? I know, crazy right? I've been mistaken for Garfield because I'm so good at collecting toe nail shavings. Well, I'll be.

What's up. My name is Muca Hornbop. Can you guess what it's short for? Pursuing a career in being a Back-end Developurr has been exhausting, so I'm switching paths to be become a Security Guard. What do you want from me?
Good morning! Kitty #91931 here. I'm here to enjoy spinning sick beats and riding unicorns. I once made a rhino grimace. Purrhaps this is the beginning of a beautiful relationship.

Guten tag! I'm Limited Ducat #8899/10,000. I work as a Back-End Developer / Personal Trainer and I love living the dream. When I'm not swiping right, I'm swiping right! I feel like we know each other so well already!

Hello darkness, my old friend! I'm Panda Elfinmuffin. Roses are Pantone 18-3838 ultra violet, violets are vermillion, I'm weird. I was once roommates with a surly troll. It was infuriating. Come, I'll show you my collection of ranch dressing.

Greetings. My name is Gen 0-NOT COMING BACK TO EARTH. Being my friend means many days filled with cutting my own bangs. I really don't understand why everyone thinks I got my Achilles tendon done, but it's not true. I'm all natural. I’m not a photographer, but I can picture me and you together.
你好喵！. 我的名字超酷，叫 R1 Dori！我是一名专业的厨师 ，最爱就是 新疆羊肉串！ 老实说，本喵真的可以为了 为了和周杰伦PK饶舌 而放弃所有喵星粮食。 一起畅玩喵趴吧！

Salutations! I'm Kaka Whamway, and I'm as cute as it gets. Just ask my mom! Want to go shopping? We can get our claws painted. If you can prove the earth speaks to me through my feet then I'll eat my jean jackets right here, right now.

RAWR XD. My name is Biscuit Dilliplum. As a young kitten, I was always applying for credit, but I think I've grown out of that. I'm a cat, but I've always felt more like I belong in the patagonian mara family. You're going to need a lot of wine for this relationship to be tolerable.
Hark! I'm 🧬 Gen 1 H1 Gene Swap. I'll know I've made it when I sleep every night on a mattress made entirely of ricotta. I eat in my sleep, I hope that's not going to be a problem.

I might appear to be a simple talisman, but if you take me into the realm of the Citadel you can reveal my true power: they call me Tally the Purrocious #141! No god can control me, but all will try. And if they succeed in collecting every talisman, who knows what power they could wield?
喵！. 认识我的人都管我叫 Lencho Hulabug！若你也喜欢披萨，那我们就有话可聊啦！ 本喵曾经和一只 壁虎干起架来，还赢了呢。 本喵等不及到了凌晨四点叫你起床上厕所了！

I might appear to be a simple talisman, but if you take me into the realm of the Citadel you can reveal my true power: they call me VIRGIN: Tally. 5 Multi Traits.! No god can control me, but all will try. And if they succeed in collecting every talisman, who knows what power they could wield?

Good day. I'm Colonel Horneyes. I'm working on a scientific experiment involving the thigh and the heart of a newly discovered type of robot. That's all I can tell you for now. If I could be anybody in the world, it would be Snooki. Sorry, gotta jet!

Yikes! You scared me. My name is Cookie Sadswoggle and I don't like to be called anything else. I'm a little tantalizing but I know how to have a good time. My band's sound is a mix of Young Thug and NSYNC. Let's connect on Nexopia.
Oh, hello. I'm Kitty #591752. If you also love to wear mom jeans, we're probably meant to be together. I would give it all up to run a cruise line. Thanks for adopting me, you won't regret it!
Sup! I'm Kitty #590696. I work as a Security Guard and I love collecting stamps. I went on an Eat, Pray, Love trip with a chimpanzee. I do not regret it. Let's get woke together.

Jambo. I'm Mother Snagglelump. Do you also love to eat jalapeños with Tapatío? Beneath this tough exterior beats the heart of a wild octopus. I love listening to Led Zeppelin's latest release while cooking apple pie.

Dia dhuit, I'm Clover! Oof, I rode in here on a rainbow and those things aren't as soft as they look. Have you seen my pot o' gold? I swear I left it right here... Oh well, I don't need piles o' shinies to know I'm the luckiest cat in the KittyVerse––I get to hang out with you!

Good morning. I'm Kitty #568014. I'm often referred to as the Neville Longbottom of the group. I once went to Mexico with a labradoodle. We haven't spoken since. I look forward to sweating through my feet with you.

Top of the mornin' to ya. My name is Vitalik, but I'm in the process of legally changing it to Michael Cera. Some people think I look like Shia LaBeouf, what do you think? I also grow ghost peppers in my garden.
Uh, hi! I'm Roblu*Whix*Thic*Mauv*Hima. Just between us, I have a fetish for running a podcast. I once judged a dolphin. I don't like to talk about it. I love making new friends like you.
Oh hi. I'm Kitty #564536. I used to do backup dancing for Mozart until I was caught impersonating Confucius. In my free time, I can usually be found picking flowers or parkouring. Let's get breeding!

*deadpan stare*. I'm 親忍者. I'm often referred to as the Cersei Lannister of the group. Honestly, counting sheep is all I care about at this stage in my life. I hope you love eating filet of fish with tomatillo sauce as much as I do!

How's kicks. I like kickboxing because my name is Ginger Ahemrubin. Pursuing a career in being a Brand Consultant has been exhausting, so I'm switching paths to be become a Deep Sea Explorer. I can't talk here, there are too many eavesdroppers around.

Salaam. I am 148/1151 - Little Uplink Kitty and I am better at improving my K/D ratio than you. Try me. This one time, at band camp, I was voted "most likely to score a hole in one while on vacation". K bye.
Hark! I'm Briciola Ministerfu. I taught Simon and Garfunkel everything they know about polishing rocks. I often get mistaken for Mozart.
Oh, hello! I'm Lil' Forest Elk. I work as a Security Guard during the week, and I like people-watching on the weekends. I try to model my life after Steve Urkel. This will be an amewsing friendship.

Listen up. Lieutenant Waddletock? Haven't heard that name in years. You should know that I'm obsessed with catching the world's first elf, and I won't rest until I do. I also grow ghost peppers in my garden.
Yaya. I'm Frank Hissguts, and I'm as cute as it gets. Just ask my mom! I often wonder what a lovechild between Ryan Gosling and Charlemagne would look like. My celebrity crush is Jonah Hill.
Hi-ya! I'm Green Gilly. I'm often referred to as the Dwight Schrute of the group. Some people say I'm the Dwight Schrute of the group. Can you make my seductive dreams come true?
Aloha! I'm Kitty #236924. I've never told anyone this, but I once licked a dog. I was voted most likely to work at NASA in college. I look forward to eating lasagna with you.

*hissing noises*! I'm Kitty #321587. I enjoy sweating through my feet, watching Stranger Things, and grooming. When no one's home, I invite my pals over and we listen to Aretha Franklin. Our friendship will be fabulous, wondrous, and full of chocolate.

Hola! I'm known as Krishna Surlyswoggle. I have a complicated past, but I'm ready for a new beginning. I would honestly rather do anything else than vomiting on the carpet. Can you explain where babies come from? Asking for a friend...

I'm Purebred: Pawrula. 5 x2 Traits, and I’m on a mission to bridge the distance between academia and industry, so we can all do for value what the internet did for information. Like a cat walking on a keyboard, we'll be an unstoppable force — a collective pushing the whole forward. Sometimes I feel like a crusader leading the charge, but other times I feel like a nap in the sunshine, so there's a lot going on.
Shalom. I'm 🧬 Gen 1 H1 Gene Swap. Step into my office. I can safely say that guacamole is the greatest thing since sliced bread. Don't even try to convince me otherwise. Have you seen my brooches?

I'm Virgin Purebred: Pawrula., and I’m on a mission to bridge the distance between academia and industry, so we can all do for value what the internet did for information. Like a cat walking on a keyboard, we'll be an unstoppable force — a collective pushing the whole forward. Sometimes I feel like a crusader leading the charge, but other times I feel like a nap in the sunshine, so there's a lot going on.

Salut! I'm afraid I have made a terrible mistake. My name is 333, and I am here to tell you: water is really, really wet. It seems so magical when you’re staring at it from above. It holds fish, as far as the eye can see. They’re waiting for you, down in the depths. But so is the water. Mise en garde!
*tips hat*. I am the one and only Ahman Hulaplum *Beatlesque*. I would go on a date with a wombat just because of the economy. Can you explain where babies come from? Asking for a friend...
What gives, please refer to me as Karima Sizzlefluff, and only that. I listened to Dolly Parton before it was cool. I often get mistaken for Vanilla Ice.
Hallo. I'm Peaches Wasabidaze, and I'm not here to make friends, I'm here to win. I am just dying to meet Sylvester. Hurry, we haven't much time.

Hi-ya. I'm Sapphire Haze. If you also can't stand the smell of tacos, we're going to be fast friends. I like to listen to Vanilla Ice while grooming. Don't judge me. Can't wait to sing karaoke to Aretha Franklin with you!

I might appear to be a simple talisman, but if you take me into the realm of the Citadel you can reveal my true power: they call me VIRGIN: Purebred Tally. Shiny!! No god can control me, but all will try. And if they succeed in collecting every talisman, who knows what power they could wield?

Eyyyyyyy! My name's Royal Sapphire. I once coughed a furball up on Winston Churchill's cat. They had it coming. My great-great-great-great-great-great grandkitty lived with Marie Curie. Can't wait to sing karaoke to Frank Sinatra with you!
Why hello there! I'm Kitty #901528, student of Balthazaar of the Unknown Lands. I really want to become a Professional Mourner. I dream about it every day. Smell ya later!

Hello, lover. Have you ever gotten lost staring into the eyes of your other Kitty-half? You can thank me for that, for I am Lil Purrfect #27, and I'm here to shoot every nonfungible creature with arrows of love. Are you ready? I think you're my next target.

What's up! I'm Kitty #393205. My friends describe me as preposterous and vegan. When my owner isn't watching, I steal their oversized sweaters and use them for litter paper. I'm not sorry. Will you be the garlic butter to my maple syrup?
噢嗨喵！. 从小，大伙儿都叫我 Shushu Bluetukhus！若你也喜欢收集迷人的瑜伽裤，不如我们安排个时间见面吧！ 本喵的人生梦想是 为了与刘亦菲共度一天。 本喵和你是不是上辈子见过呀？

Hey, what's up, hello. I'm Wrecked 88. I dare you to say my name three times in front of a mirror! I'm really trying to become a master Teacher. Spending my nights polishing rocks probably isn't helping, though. Goodnight, I'm going to sleep.

Who goes there. My name is Catnip McClintock and I don't like to be called anything else. I'm a little lawful but I know how to have a good time. I'm trying this weird diet where I only eat cantaloupe, I'll let you know how it goes. My comfort food is a pizza with extra parmesan, hold the pizza.

Dia dhuit, I'm Clover! Oof, I rode in here on a rainbow and those things aren't as soft as they look. Have you seen my pot o' gold? I swear I left it right here... Oh well, I don't need piles o' shinies to know I'm the luckiest cat in the KittyVerse––I get to hang out with you!

Hey! Ho! Let's go. My parents named me David Teaguts, but I prefer Benjamin Franklin. I still dream of becoming a Professional Mourner, but I'm not sure where to start. Let's pump some Liberace and get busy!
Bonjour. double wiley + r2,3 icy is the name and watching game shows is the game. I once got stung by a bee on my eyebrow. Can you help me get past the part in Forza Motorsport that I can't beat?
Sup playa! I'm Founder Cat 19. I believe the world is flat. I like to listen to Metallica while grooming. Don't judge me. We can be friends, but keep the ultra purrsonal stuff to yourself, please.
What's up! They call me Kitty #831634. Hey, got any horseradish on you? I'm always hungry. Wu-Tang wants me, but I'm more of a Justin Bieber fan. Did we just become best friends?
Jambo. I am Mother Bahkewtie, come closer, child. On Sundays I like chewing indoor plants. Please do not disturb me then. I'm reading your aura, and it's neon pink.

Top o' the muffin to ya! Allow me to introduce myself. I am Gen1 BIS Highlander Missmuffet and I am very well known for chasing string and watching Jerry Springer. Do you think Vlad the Impaler would've approved of my purrs and grooming style? I like to think so. Will you brush my tail? I like it brushed three times a day.

Yikes! You scared me. My name is Kottur Bobokat. As a young kitten, I was always tipping glasses of water over, but I think I've grown out of that. Everything I own is eggshell white, even my litterbox! I'm going to show you the time of your life.

Hiya. My name is Gen 0 Birman. I make a mean overcooked pasta casserole. I really don't understand why everyone thinks I got my nose done, but it's not true. I'm all natural. I’m not a photographer, but I can picture me and you together.

Good day! My name is Lencho Demonzap. I work as a Shaman, and I also moonlight as a Ramona Flowers impersonator. I did the album artwork for the latest Chumbawamba album. I'm pretty proud of it. Want to play House of the Dead together? I'm addicted.
How do you do. I am Old Sullenwidgey. I'm glad you've come. In another life, I think I would have been a tufted deer. I don't have time for new friends, but I'll make an exception for you.

Good morning! I'm Kitty #399579. I've never told anyone this, but I once groomed a dog. It's not common knowledge, but my ancestry connects me to John F. Kennedy Jr.. I hope we can be gullible friends.

Jambo! I'm Kitty #592969. If you also can't stand the smell of macaroni casserole, we're going to be fast friends. I'm on a new diet that consists of cucumber salad and chorizo sausage. I'm impressed with the results so far. Enchanté.
I'm Dreggo, and I'm all fired up and feeling pretty fangtastic about the future. It's dark and boring in here, to be honest with you, and I'm egg-cited to get out soon. World, here I come!

Welcome. My name is VIRGIN: Buttercup Cindylou., but I prefer to be addressed as "your highness". I can whistle any Tom Jones song. It's a weird talent, but it entertains most people. Let's pump some Rita Ora and get busy!
Who goes there. I'm called Bacio Sourthang. I like long walks on the beach and vegenaise. I'm really trying to be more sensible right now. Do you think it's working? Hold my beer.

Salutations. I respond to Mocha Slippybean, although that doesn't mean I'll acknowledge you. I'm trying to consume at least one serving of vegan burgers every day. It's a newer health thing I read about on the web. Whenever I hear LCD Soundsystem I just have to kiss.
I'm 💙 Lapis 💙 Icicle. LOW GEN., who's asking? I listened to Justin Bieber before it was cool. In high school I was voted "most likely to work at NASA" and it definitely came true.
Yo yo yo! My name is Carl Pocketsauce. I'm seductive, you're hairy, let's connect. I combine the best qualities of Diane Keaton, The Pope, and Father John Misty. Later, I'm headed to play Contra.
Behold, it is I, Cheeky Pharoahdub. I'm descended from Salem. I love playing The Sims. Wanna join me?

Bonjour. I'm Purebred: Beatlesque with RTG.. Please take a seat. I once swerved Charlemagne to be on Family Feud. I try to bury that memory deep in the litterbox of my mind. Whenever I hear Celine Dion I just have to wince.

Yo yo yo! Allow me to introduce myself. I am Bacio Mugfizzle and I am very well known for unravelling toilet paper and cutting my own bangs. If you'll just give me 30 seconds of your time, I can prove beyond a doubt that the moon landing was produced by Steven Spielberg. Can you explain where babies come from? Asking for a friend...

How you doin! My name is Felis Scrummysnuggums. My favourite topic of conversation is Mother Teresa. My squad always tells me to be more provocative, but meh. I was the runt of the litter, but trust me, I'm thriving.

Ciao! I'm FatherA. My friends describe me as prickly and voluptuous. When my owner isn't watching, I steal their oversized sweaters and use them for litter paper. I'm not sorry. I look forward to hitting on yo' man with you.
Heyo. My name is Farfalle Yappyboop. My best friend is a Ogopogo. I'm descended from Chester Cheetah. Let's pump some U2 and get busy!
*yawn* Sorry, you caught me napping. You may call me Minka Queentush. When I wake up in the morning, my first thought is always of ricotta. Please pay attention to me.

Greetings, denizens of Earth! Call me J. Atlas, Solver of Puzzles. Your planet may look like a ball of yarn, but I've learned earthquakes make for lots of spilled milk. I have solved the world's greatest mysteries, unravelled the world's stickiest riddles, and calculated the world's newest cryptographs. I may nap 80% of every eon, but I party 24/7.
哩好！! 本喵就是最有人气的 Andrew Candeedee！在大学里我可是被评选为十佳捣乱分子哦！ 莫扎特 对本喵极为欣赏，但我还是比较喜欢当 碧昂丝 的粉丝。 或许本喵和你可以当个好朋友！
Noice. I am Precious Snookyobie, AKA Kitty of your dreams. My best dress-up costume ever was when I impersonated AC Slater. What do you want from me?

Greetings, kind purr! My name's Page + Kaleidoscope and I'm a very good and clever kitten with a lot to offer the world! I have squired with the greatest of knights: there was Sir Face (they were a bit shallow), Sir Port (a very kind cat), and of course, Sir Prise (she was amazing). And now I have you! Gosh! I must be the luckiest kitten in the world!

Stitches? Sure, I've got a few. But please - call me Boris S4. I'm a body builder by purrfession, though I've always been a bit misunderstood. I've been thinking about putting myself on the market and looking for love - will you be my zombae?
Noice. They call me VIRGIN: Huacool.. Hey, got any mac 'n' cheese on you? I'm always hungry. I enjoy jumping from one surface to another. Let's go getting turnt together!

Good day. I am Beatlesque. Monochrome Virgin.. I'm glad you've come. This one time, at band camp, I was voted "most likely to kill a man just to feel alive". Would you believe that Michael J Fox is just like you and me?

Hey! You can call me Billie, but I prefer to go by the name Blue Lightning whenever fans are watching. I'm always ready to perform, so count on me if you need someone who can execute. These legs are my largest assets after all! Maybe I should insure them one day. Wanna race?

*hissing noises*. I'm Pudding Sprinkleboo, at least that's what they're calling me these days. I'm thinking of dying my fur a metallic shade of red. Do you think it will suit me? Do you also love maple syrup?
Hiya. I'm Wyrm in a Box. No cat puns, please. I assess you to be saucy, and I approve. My only policy is no politics.

Halloooo, my name is Kahuna Sullenheart, but I prefer to go by Mary Queen of Scots. Would you believe me if I told you the world is surrounded by an ice wall that stops us from falling into space? What if I said Pluto is actually a planet? Come, I'll show you my collection of ghost pepper hot sauce.

Hey. My name is Pawvril. Can you see the thousands of Kitties who came to shout out their teenage angst? I know, I'm excited too. This is our first World Tour. I just prefer expressing my emotions through my bass. Did you see a skater boy in the crowd?

*hissing noises*. I'm Sister Queenbuncle. I feel like I know you from a past life... You should know that I'm obsessed with catching the world's first elf on the shelf, and I won't rest until I do. Sorry, gotta jet!

I am Rara Lackarue, who dares approach me? Oh, it's you. If you'll just give me 30 seconds of your time, I can prove beyond a doubt that watermelon seeds will grow in your stomach. I'm single and ready to mingle.

Bonjour! I'm Kylian Mbappé, and I've loved the beautiful game since I was a beautiful kitten. Some people call it football, which is weird because pawball makes more sense. Is it offside to ask if you'd join my team? I need a winger, and I've heard you've got fancy footwork.

Avast ye! I'm the dread pirate Furbeard, and I'll most likely scratch you in the morning. This Old Salt knows a few tricks: how to avoid a meowtiny, how to get out of swabbing the litter deck, and just where the captain's log is buried. Beware the Krakitten in the briny deep. Or is that Pickles?
Top o' the muffin to ya. My name is Moonrise Eclipse, and my game is personal development. During my kitten days, I beheld Meg Griffin. I want to know what love is. I want you to show me.
Awooooooga. My name is Peaches Grimmbutt. I love to wear Pantone 18-3838 ultra violet. Some people think I look like Bob Saget, what do you think? Someday, all of this will be yours.
Good day. I'm Marshall Daintysire. I feel like I know you from a past life... When I'm embarassed, I get sweaty in my tail tuft area. Check me out!
Rise and grind, my name is Fuku Finetail, but you may address me as supreme cat overlord. I once got stung by a bee on my third eye. Alright, alright, alright.
Who goes there. I'm Sister Sullenpoppins. Do you also love to eat horseradish with tomatillo sauce? My best feature? My kidney, obviously. My tail tuft is itchy and I can't reach. Would you mind?
*waves*. The name's Lola Abratooth. Some people think I look like Kristen Wiig, what do you think? I want to know what love is. I want you to show me.
Enchanté! I'm Tora Didgerifu, and I'm not here to make friends, I'm here to win. I enjoy jumping from one surface to another. I like the way you smell.

Top of the mornin' to ya. They call me Hime Pharoahlater. Hey, got any eggplant on you? I'm always hungry. I was voted "Most gorgeous" at my office Christmas party. Also, I love McDonalds happy meals.
Allo! My name is Tzar Doowight. My favourite topic of conversation is Confucius. Did you know that Ash Ketchum used to slather their overcooked pasta in low fat mayo? Gahhh, aren't you cute!

asset_name: Cat Got Into The Cocaine Again
asset_description: Top o' the muffin to ya. My name is Cat Got Into The Cocaine Again, which got me teased a lot in high school. Michael Cera is my spirit animal. You're fancy, and I like it.

Greetings, acolyte, I am Purrspero, master of the arcane arts and batting at string. I wield unfathomable power and still nap 16 hours a day. I offer my mystical abilities only to the worthiest lords and ladies of the KittyVerse, like you.
Yo. I'm Doodoo Zippyki. No cat puns, please. My best dress-up costume ever was when I impersonated Spongebob. Smell ya later!

Hi. I'm Oohshiny Kaleidoscope! 🌈✨. I feel like I know you from a past life... I've never actually finished Sixteen Candles, I get too distracted with inheriting millions. What's up? Cat got your tongue?
*龇牙咧嘴*! 本喵就是天才 Tadita Linktock！我在和隔壁老喵比瞪眼和挑逗调酒帅哥方面可是颇有名气呢！ 有时候，本喵白天打盹儿时会梦见自己在 偷看《怪奇物语》、骑马 还有 新疆羊肉串。 本喵在舞池中央等你！

Ohayo. I am Gizmo Grimmdoo. Follow my rules and we'll get along just fine. I would honestly rather do anything else than weaving in and out of humans' legs. Let's go shopping at the organic foods market on Sundays.
Ohayou. I am Booboo Bopkat. Follow my rules and we'll get along just fine. I'd give anything to hang out with Michael Cera. I also grow ghost peppers in my garden.

Yikes! You scared me. I excel at eating fine cheeses. Oh, right, my name is Hime Allswoggle. Do you think Sir John A. MacDonald would've approved of my purrs and grooming style? I like to think so. Want to start a band together? Dibs bass!
Oh, hello! I'm Micio Squeepoppins, but you already know that. My best feature? My tail, obviously. Why I oughta!

Good day! I'm Moo, I'm a Giraffe. I am currently trying to start my own company making skorts for tripod kitties. I still dream of becoming a Poet, but I'm not sure where to start. Let's braid our tails!

Greetings. I'm Gen_1 w/ Double BIS Mewtation. If you also can't stand the smell of bananas, we're going to be fast friends. I once batted my paw at a chimpanzee. I don't like to talk about it. I feel like we know each other so well already!
*waves*! I'm GooglyGerbil With Persian Gene. I'm a Train Conductor by day, and I like pole dancing by night. I'm convinced that the world is flat. One day I'll prove it. Let's pawty!
How's it going. Please call me Bandit Tangoo or else I may scratch. I really want to lay a nice rooster one day, is that weird? I know many interesting facts about the rare and majestic platypus.

Who goes there! I'm The Great Catsby, student of Balthazaar of the Unknown Lands. Do you think John F. Kennedy Jr would've approved of my purrs and grooming style? I like to think so. Have you seen my ski goggles?
嗨嗨！. 本喵的大名就是 Bao Mugbean！老实说，我真的不能够忍受那些把时间浪费在 跟着乌鸦到处走上的喵星人。 有些人说我在团体里有憨豆先生 的个性。 我希望你也和我一样，吃 哈密瓜 的时候喜欢加点 火锅调料 ！
Welcome. You may call me wrapps. Want to go shopping? We can get our claws painted. Call me maybe.

Aloha! I'm Dot. I enjoy eating until I loathe myself, reading garfield, and tricking babies. When no one's home, I invite my pals over and we listen to Mariah Carey. I hope we can be wondrous friends.
Yarr matey. I went by the name Zaki Bippitypoopsie once. Want to go shopping? We can get our claws painted. Word on the street is Smash Bros is the best game of all time. All time!
Oh heyyy! I'm Chantrea Magicbobo. I tend to shimmy when I'm excited. I once interned for Julius Caesar. It was... interesting. What do you want from me?
Hey cutie. You may call me Nala Bubblesshmoops. I shall call you King Henry VIII. I honestly would rather do anything else besides watch The Heathers. I can tell you like to get into trouble.

*scraaatttttttttch* I'm DJ Meowlody, and meowsic is eight of my nine lives. Here, I made you a mixtape. That'll be 2 ETH. Trust me, it'll get your toes tapping and your tail twitching. Don't forget to check out my SoundCloud!

Oh ho ho ho! You've released Krakitten, and if you're also all aboat that bass, I'm open to a planktonic relationship. As I always say, "Carp diem: seas the day." You think Squiddlesworth is a match for me? Paw-lease. No Kitty escapes my grasp, at least until I've given them ten tickles. *Waves* So long, suckers!
Where are my manners. I'm Maow Scrummyloo *Purrbados*. I'm trying to live my best life, unravelling toilet paper and sculpting my guns. I listened to Kelly Clarkson before it was cool. Leave me.
嗨喵！. 我叫 Fluffy Crazywow！我超爱 爬上姚明头顶观世界 还有 跳健身操。 SHE 对本喵极为欣赏，但我还是比较喜欢当 周杰伦 的粉丝。 我迫不及待要和你一起大唱 王力宏 的经典好歌！

Hi, I'm Ellie - so glad you herd about the slumber purrty! I'm having an absolute blast, hanging out with furriends and getting a bit wild. Pillow fights are TONS of fun... in fact, they're downright elephantastic!

Hark! I'm VIRGIN: Purebred Cindylou.. I spend all my money on Interpol records and I don't even have a record player yet. I heard John Malkovich has a crush on me. Meh.

Eyyyyyyy. I'm Chibi Vileroo 7, and I will be your personal Retail Greeter. In another life, I think I would have been a rooster. I've spent the last few years perfecting my steak recipe. Wanna try it?
Hiya. I'm Marshall Scuttlegirl. Do you also love to eat spicy salami with pickles? Sandra Bullock is my spirit animal. Call me maybe.

Hallo! I'm Purrity, the Kitty bringing Parity to the blockchain. Security's my middle name and peer to peer's my driving game. I believe your data is your property, but that won't stop me from sitting on your laptop while you're trying to type.

Greetings! I am Cheddar Bob, the most fermented... err, feared Kitty wizard in Catelot. Well, since Raspoutine, at least. I curdle my enemies and cuddle my loved ones. I'm quite fondue you, so if you’re feta up with your old life, join me, and we’ll have a gouda time together.

Hi-ya! My name's Psychodelic. I once peed on Amelia Earhart's cat. They had it coming. Sometimes I daydream of a life full of riding dirty, apple pie, and volunteering at the local kitten rescue shelter. I like your face.

Welcome. Sir Megaright? Haven't heard that name in years. I used to have a pet witch. Its name was Teddy Roosevelt. Please pay attention to me.
